title: Xbox Vs America
description:
Xbox, well, specifically, Microsoft, has been going up against the FTC for a while now.

And finally, we’ve got a trial.

Some things were said, and I’m gonna talk about some of those things.

Not all of them.

But a few.

Sony and PlayStation seem kinda angry, but not that angry.

Real exciting stuff.
